  "description": "A breathtaking view of a bay or coastline bathed in the golden light of either sunrise or sunset. Dramatic, low-hanging clouds obscure the upper portion of the scene, with radiant beams of light piercing through the cloud cover and reflecting brilliantly on the water's surface. Silhouetted trees and foliage frame the lower portion of the image, adding depth and a sense of foreground. The coastline itself appears as a dark, curving shape in the distance, hinting at hills or mountains. The overall composition evokes a serene and majestic feeling.",
